		(property "Description" "Arduino Nano board based on the ESP32-S3 with a dual-core 240 MHz processor, 384 kB ROM, 512 kB SRAM. Operates at 3.3V, with 5V USB-C® input and 6-21V VIN. Features Wi-Fi®, Bluetooth® LE, digital and analog pins, and supports SPI, I2C, UART, I2S, and CAN."
